00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:38,450
I didn't expect you to have such skills.

2
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:41,500
I've heard that in ordinary families,

3
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:43,250
the husband will help his wife

4
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:45,500
with combing her hair and drawing her eyebrows.

5
00:01:46,290 --> 00:01:47,410
I'm okay at combing hair.

6
00:01:48,370 --> 00:01:51,250
But I need more practice with drawing eyebrows.

7
00:01:52,370 --> 00:01:54,290
You're not planning to practice on my eyebrows, are you?

8
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:57,950
Have you forgotten,

9
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:59,580
I've painted your portrait for five lifetimes.

10
00:02:01,290 --> 00:02:02,790
Every time I painted you before,

11
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:04,040
it was all practice.

12
00:02:05,290 --> 00:02:08,200
But this time, I have to practice on the real person.

13
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:38,500
What's wrong?

14
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:41,250
My drawing shouldn't look that bad, right?

15
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:45,370
Xiao Jingyang.

16
00:02:46,370 --> 00:02:48,120
I like it when you draw my eyebrows.

17
00:02:49,830 --> 00:02:50,620
From now on,

18
00:02:51,830 --> 00:02:53,870
you have to draw my eyebrows for the rest of your life.

19
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:14,290
Alright.

20
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,750
I'll draw your eyebrows for the rest of my life.

21
00:03:32,950 --> 00:03:34,370
Master, look.

22
00:03:34,370 --> 00:03:35,580
These are flowers Jingyang gave me.

23
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:36,660
Aren't they pretty?

24
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:39,660
Perfect timing.

25
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:42,040
Separate out the flowers and herbs here that can be used as medicine.

26
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:44,830
How long has it been since you reviewed your lessons?

27
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:47,910
Master, you're just jealous.

28
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,000
Jingyang.

29
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,870
Master, how is he?

30
00:04:10,580 --> 00:04:11,830
He's at the end of his strength.

31
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:17,500
I'm afraid he won't make it through today.

32
00:04:28,290 --> 00:04:30,080
From the moment you brought him here,

33
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:33,410
I already knew this day would come.

34
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,290
Mingxuan.

35
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:38,200
This past month

36
00:04:39,410 --> 00:04:42,700
has already been the most time he could have.

37
00:04:45,450 --> 00:04:46,290
As your master,

38
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,500
there's nothing more I can do.

39
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:09,330
Xiao Jingyang

40
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:14,700
I thought this life would last a bit longer.

41
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:16,830
Ming Xuan

42
00:05:18,700 --> 00:05:19,830
I'm fine.

43
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,330
Don't cry.

44
00:05:27,290 --> 00:05:28,660
You promised me.

45
00:05:29,790 --> 00:05:32,330
That we'd watch the sunrise and sunset together.

46
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:35,910
That you'd go see the mountains and rivers with me.

47
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:38,870
That you'd go with me

48
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:41,040
to revisit the places we used to stay.

49
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:44,040
All of these,

50
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,580
you haven't done.

51
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:48,620
Yeah.

52
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:52,660
We still have so many

53
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:56,500
things we haven't done.

54
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:15,620
I have to break my promise on the other things.

55
00:06:18,540 --> 00:06:20,660
At least I can still watch one more sunset with you.

56
00:06:22,330 --> 00:06:25,580
No, you didn't break your promise.

57
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:30,080
I'll go see the mountains and rivers for you.

58
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:33,120
I'll walk our path again.

59
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,620
Okay.

60
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,290
Go see them for me.

61
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:58,950
Xiao Jingyang

62
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:02,200
I'm very happy.

63
00:07:04,450 --> 00:07:07,450
Happy that you didn't push me away in this life.

64
00:07:10,790 --> 00:07:12,410
I was selfish too.

65
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:20,200
In every past life, I kept wondering

66
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:24,910
when

67
00:07:24,910 --> 00:07:27,450
I could truly have you, completely

68
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:30,870
when

69
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:37,200
I could love you openly and without fear

70
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:42,830
Even in this life, I hesitated

71
00:07:45,290 --> 00:07:46,330
I wavered

72
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,250
If you ever backed away, even once

73
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,750
I would have pushed you away

74
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,790
Mingxuan

75
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:03,870
I really want

76
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:10,620
I really want to stay by your side

77
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:15,370
I'm already content

78
00:08:17,250 --> 00:08:19,410
The time I've spent with you

79
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:23,160
feels like I've lived my whole life

80
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,040
I'm sorry

81
00:08:37,830 --> 00:08:38,950
In this life

82
00:08:41,410 --> 00:08:45,830
I can't keep walking this path with you

83
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:50,330
If there's a next life

84
00:09:00,330 --> 00:09:03,330
I'll find you as soon as I can

85
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,120
to love you

86
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,290
to cherish you

87
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:21,370
to protect you

88
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:35,450
Xiao Jingyang

89
00:09:48,250 --> 00:09:49,200
Xiao Jingyang

90
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:53,950
If there's a next life

91
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,950
I'll make sure to find you first
